sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SVC as Ingest Service
    participant WRK as Worker Pool
    participant AGG as Aggregator
    participant LLM as Modal LLM
    participant STORE as Redis/Tracker

    User->>UI: Upload PDF
    UI->>API: POST /ingest?mode=parallel|sequential
    API->>SVC: ingest_pdf()
    SVC->>STORE: quota + cache + init job
    SVC->>WRK: dispatch chunk tasks
    API-->>UI: job_id

    loop While running
        UI->>API: GET /status/{job_id}
        API->>STORE: read progress
        API-->>UI: done/total/progress_pct
    end

    WRK->>STORE: store chunk outputs
    SVC->>AGG: aggregate(job_id)
    AGG->>LLM: final synthesis
    LLM-->>AGG: structured analysis
    AGG->>STORE: final_output + done

    UI->>API: GET /result/{job_id}/markdown
    API-->>UI: markdown report